description:
Beautifully furnished 1brm apt. with exposed brick walls and contemporary classic style. 
Lots of light and storage space. 
T.V, cable, Internet available
Close to the HighLine, Meatpacking District, Chelsea art galleries, Madison Square Garden, etc. 
A couple blocks from major A, C, E, 1,2,3 and L subway lines
Best restaurants and cafes at your steps
name: Classic Contemporary entire Chelsea-Highline apt
